                The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog. This is how body text looks 
                at different breakpoints with optimal line height for readability.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Button Variants Demo -->
    <section class="container mx-auto px-5 md:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
